{"title":"cf#E49(1027)","date":"2018-08-18T16:00:00.000Z","author":"luoyayu","excerpt":"","slug":"2018-08-19-cf_E49_1027","comments":true,"tags":["codeforces"],"categories":["ACM"],"updated":"2018-08-19T02:54:02.000Z","content":"<h1 id=\"A-签到\"><a href=\"#A-签到\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"A 签到\"></a>A 签到</h1><p>注意字符必须改变(ab, xy)</p>\n<h1 id=\"B-填数-规律\"><a href=\"#B-填数-规律\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"B 填数+规律\"></a>B 填数+规律</h1><h2 id=\"做法一：分类讨论\"><a href=\"#做法一：分类讨论\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"做法一：分类讨论\"></a>做法一：分类讨论</h2><p>按(x+y)奇偶，再讨论x,y的奇偶</p>\n<h2 id=\"做法二：规律\"><a href=\"#做法二：规律\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"做法二：规律\"></a>做法二：规律</h2><p>(x+y)是偶数的位置的值全部减去右下角的值会发现其实也是1~ceil(n*n/2)的填数<br>对于这种情况其值为$\\displaystyle n\\frac{x-1}{2}+\\frac{y+1}{2}$</p>\n<h2 id=\"code\"><a href=\"#code\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"code\"></a>code</h2><iframe id=\"iFrame0\" name=\"iFrame0\" width=\"100%\" onload=\"this.height=iFrame0.document.body.scrollHeight\" frameborder=\"0\" src=\"/htmlcode/cf/cf1027b.html\" scrolling=\"no\" allowtransparency=\"yes\"></iframe>\n\n<h1 id=\"C\"><a href=\"#C\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"C\"></a>C</h1>","next":{"title":"cf#504(1023)","slug":"2018-08-18-cf_504_1023"},"link":"/2018/08/19","toc":[{"title":"A 签到","id":"A-签到","index":"1"},{"title":"B 填数+规律","id":"B-填数-规律","index":"2","children":[{"title":"做法一：分类讨论","id":"做法一：分类讨论","index":"2.1"},{"title":"做法二：规律","id":"做法二：规律","index":"2.2"},{"title":"code","id":"code","index":"2.3"}]},{"title":"C","id":"C","index":"3"}]}